{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"SharedWorkerGlobalScope: connect イベント","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/SharedWorkerGlobalScope/connect_event","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/SharedWorkerGlobalScope\"><code>SharedWorkerGlobalScope</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SharedWorkerGlobalScope/applicationCache\"><code>applicationCache</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SharedWorkerGlobalScope/name\"><code>name</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SharedWorkerGlobalScope/close\"><code>close()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>イベント</summary><ol><li><em><code>connect</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>継承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><strong><code>connect</code></strong> イベントは、新しいクライアントが接続したときに共有ワーカーの <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/SharedWorkerGlobalScope\"><code>SharedWorkerGlobalScope</code></a> に発生します。</p>\n\n<table class=\"properties\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">バブリング</th>\n   <td>なし</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">キャンセル可能</th>\n   <td>いいえ</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">インターフェイス</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MessageEvent\"><code>MessageEvent</code></a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">イベントハンドラープロパティ</th>\n   <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SharedWorkerGlobalScope/connect_event\"><code>SharedWorkerGlobalScope.onconnect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>この例は共有ワーカーファイルを示しています。メインスレッドから <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MessagePort\"><code>MessagePort</code></a> を通して Worker へのコネクションが発生したとき、 <code>onconnect</code> イベントハンドラーが呼び出されます。イベントオブジェクトは <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MessageEvent\"><code>MessageEvent</code></a> です。</p>\n\n<p>接続しようとしているポート番号は、イベントオブジェクトの <code>ports</code> 引数で参照することができます。この参照にはポートを通じて来るメッセージを扱うために割り当てられた <code>onmessage</code> ハンドラーがあり、その <code>postMessage()</code> メソッドに Worker を使用してメインスレッドにメッセージを送り返すために使用することができます。</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onconnect</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> port <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>ports<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n    port<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onmessage</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> workerResult <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Result: '</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>data<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>data<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      port<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">postMessage</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>workerResult<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n    port<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">start</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>実行している例を完成させるには、 <a class=\"external-icon external\" href=\"https://github.com/mdn/simple-shared-worker\" rel=\" noopener\">Basic shared worker example</a> (<a class=\"external-icon external\" href=\"https://mdn.github.io/simple-shared-worker/\" rel=\" noopener\">共有ワーカーを実行</a>) をご覧ください。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"addeventlistener_equivalent","title":"addEventListener による同等の処理","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/addEventListener\" title=\"addEventListener()\"><code>addEventListener()</code></a> メソッドを使用してイベントハンドラーを設定することもできます。</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'connect'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> port <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>ports<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  port<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onmessage</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> workerResult <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Result: '</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>data<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>data<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    port<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">postMessage</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>workerResult<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様書","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様書</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状態</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/indices.html#event-workerglobalscope-connect\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"ja\">connect event の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">現行の標準</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.SharedWorkerGlobalScope.connect_event","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/SharedWorkerGlobalScope/connect_event/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API/Using_web_workers\">Web Worker の使用</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/SharedWorkerGlobalScope\"><code>SharedWorkerGlobalScope</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"例","id":"examples"},{"text":"仕様書","id":"specifications"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"connect イベントは、新しいクライアントが接続したときに共有ワーカーの SharedWorkerGlobalScope に発生します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"SharedWorkerGlobalScope: connect event","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"SharedWorkerGlobalScope.onconnect","locale":"fr","native":"Français"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/sharedworkerglobalscope/connect_event","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/sharedworkerglobalscope/connect_event/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/SharedWorkerGlobalScope","title":"SharedWorkerGlobalScope"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/SharedWorkerGlobalScope/connect_event","title":"SharedWorkerGlobalScope: connect イベント"}],"pageTitle":"SharedWorkerGlobalScope: connect イベント - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}